Webpage:https://httpd.apache.org/

Step1 : sudo apt-get update
Step2 : sudo apt-get install apache2
Step3 : sudo apt-get install net-tools
Step4 : netstat -a | more
Step5 : netstat -an | more
Step6 : sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 stop
Step7 : sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 start
Step8 : ab -c 20 -n 1000 http://localhost/

For verbose logging the following command can be executed:
ab -c 20 -n 1000 -e "benchmark1.csv" -v 2  http://localhost/

More information about ab tool can be found at the following website: https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/programs/ab.html


For changing the Listen configuration we can refer to the following website : https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/bind.html
